ong-bak 3 ( thai : องค์บาก 3 ) is a 2010 thai martial arts film directed , produced and written by tony jaa and panna rittikrai .   the film 's story is a follow-up to ong bak 2 , where tien ( tony jaa ) is put to be brutally beaten by lord rajasena ( sarunyu wongkrajang ) 's men .   he is helped to recover by master bua ( nirut sirijanya ) , and when tien returns to his village , he finds it taken over by bhuti sangkha ( dan chupong ) .